data.description: Experience the allure of this contemporary residence nestled in the vibrant city of Bellflower, CA. Welcome to 9735 Rose, a remarkable home that awaits its second owner, offering an exceptional living experience.With 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and 1911 square feet of space, this home exudes timeless elegance and modern charm. The open floor plan fills the interior with an abundance of natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.Step into the expansive living room, where an electric fireplace sets the perfect ambiance for cozy moments with loved ones. The dining area seamlessly connects with the family room, adorned with designer light fixtures and a stylish ceiling fan, providing an ideal space for entertaining or relaxation.The well-designed kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring ample cabinet storage, exquisite granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Its seamless flow connects to the family room, ensuring you can engage with guests while preparing meals.Upstairs, you'll discover two spacious bedrooms, offering versatility and comfort for individuals of all ages. The master bedroom retreat is a true sanctuary, boasting a walk-in closet and a grand master bathroom with His and Her vanities, a soothing soaking tub, and a resort-style showeran oasis to unwind and rejuvenate.This modern home showcases a harmonious blend of durability and beauty, with wood plank tile, laminate, and ceramic tile flooring. Additional features include central air and heat, LED recessed lights, an oversized two-car garage with direct access, an inside laundry area, and a private side and back yard.Be the proud second owner of this exceptional home, where cherished memories are waiting to be made. Don't miss out on this unmissable opportunity to own a home that perfectly blends style, comfort, and convenience.
